## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="4409a-103">Le <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationManager> classe vous permet aux accès ordinateur, application et les informations de configuration utilisateur.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4409a-103">The <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationManager> class enables you to access machine, application, and user configuration information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4409a-104">Cette classe remplace le <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSettings> (classe), qui est déconseillée.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4409a-104">This class replaces the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSettings> class, which is deprecated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4409a-105">Pour les applications web, utilisez la <xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebConfigurationManager> classe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4409a-105">For web applications, use the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebConfigurationManager> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4409a-106">Pour utiliser le <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationManager> (classe), votre projet doit référencer le `System.Configuration` assembly.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4409a-106">To use the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationManager> class, your project must reference the `System.Configuration` assembly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4409a-107">Par défaut, certains modèles de projet, comme Application de Console, ne référencent pas cet assembly afin de vous devez référencer manuellement.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4409a-107">By default, some project templates, like Console Application, do not reference this assembly so you must manually reference it.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="4409a-108">Le nom et l’emplacement du fichier de configuration d’application dépendent hôte de l’application.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4409a-108">The name and location of the application configuration file depend on the application's host.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4409a-109">Pour plus d’informations, consultez [NIB : fichiers de Configuration d’Application](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/0d05b1b8-b18b-43d8-bb3c-526ff0c44fe0).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4409a-109">For more information, see [NIB: Application Configuration Files](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/0d05b1b8-b18b-43d8-bb3c-526ff0c44fe0).</span></span>  
  
